sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Player
    participant OS as Mobile OS
    participant App as Unity app
    participant Sim as OfflineSim
    participant UI as Resume UI

    P->>OS: Sends app to background
    OS->>App: OnApplicationPause(true)
    App->>App: Persist save + timestamp Tsleep

    Note over P,OS: Hours pass...

    P->>OS: Reopens app
    OS->>App: OnApplicationPause(false)
    App->>Sim: Δt = now − Tsleep
    Sim->>Sim: Δt = min(Δt, napCap = 12h)
    Sim->>Sim: Fast-sim N ticks<br/>(economy + passive income)
    Sim-->>App: Resources delta
    App->>UI: Show "While you were away…"
    UI-->>P: +N mass, +M currency
